rComments: Interesting class, makes effective parallels between civil law and common law and really got students to think about those differences. Great introduction to the common law through historical/philosophical/case law. Very approachable and will help as much as possible if you just ask.

Intelligent though he may be, the may is an insufferable intellectual snob who is ill-equipped to teach a university class. An entire hour and a half spent listening to his rambling lectures in his quiet monotonous voice could drive anyone mad.
